  "title": "Things You Should Set Up First",
  "content": "If you're working with an existing brand, we recommend setting up a Brand Kit before generating to ensure on-brand output. A Brand Kit stores your logo, colors, fonts, and design guidance globally, and will be applied to every creative task based on your needs. You can create a separate Brand Kit for each brand you work on.\n\nJump to Brand Kit for the full feature page, including editing and per-plan limits.",
